303
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:09,920
Good!

304
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,520
Second,

305
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:22,160
the National Foreign Affairs Association

306
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:23,360
sent out a notice

307
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,880
that the National Assembly

308
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,840
