309
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,600
We are to boycott the Paris Peace Treaty.

310
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,040
Peking University,

311
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:32,800
along with students from other schools,

312
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:36,080
will be the main force in this demonstration.

313
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,360
Third is that,

314
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:40,560
the whole country has taken action.

