316
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:42,960
Shanghai.

317
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:43,840
Guangzhou.

318
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,840
Through different approaches,

319
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:46,800
they all

