329
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:07,920
He shall only concentrate on enlightenment.

330
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:09,920
Well, now he realized

331
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,640
that he was biased back then.

332
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:15,280
Given the fact that science and democracy

333
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,040
