357
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,880
Did he ask for people's opinions?

358
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,160
No.

359
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,760
Even the Chinese delegation

360
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:20,000
