361
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:22,480
A total liar.

362
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,920
The people was deceived.

363
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,520
The people was fooled.

364
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:26,960
So I said

