However, there is another way to see it.

367
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,440
There can be a good aspect.

368
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,440
How so?

369
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:35,040
Because of this Paris Peace Conference,

370
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,280
the Chinesep people are now awake.

371
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:39,440
If China wants to develop,

372
00:16:39,680 --> 00:16:41,360
