373
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:42,880
We also need to stand out,

374
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,640
fight against imperialism,

375
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,960
defend our own sovereignty.

376
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,640
To achieve these,

377
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,560
