378
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:54,320
Only when the people wake up can China have hope.

379
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,560
So, my fellow students.

380
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,680
Our lecture group on civilian education

381
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:03,200
