395
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:30,320
We are giving a series of speeches in Changxindian and other places respectively.

396
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:31,920
We are organizing a demonstration right now.

397
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:33,520
At the National Convention on May 7th,

398
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:36,160
there will be a demonstration of 100,000 people.

399
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,840
Good!

400
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:40,880
Students.

401
00:17:41,360 --> 00:17:43,760
